Direct Known Subclasses:
CloseMapAction, ExitAction, NewMapAction, OpenMapAction, OpenRecentAction
public abstract class AbstractFileAction
extends javax.swing.AbstractAction

This abstract file action asks to save the map if it has been modified. It should be subclassed by any action that would discard the currently loaded map.
